Using "RC_Core.rcm"
; Spawn-init for the Orc Warlord mini-boss (Test Zone). Runs once at spawn (the
; spawn's `script` slot, like Init_WoundedScout / Spawn_Test). Gives the boss a
; unique name — without this an NPC's name defaults to its Race ("Orc").
;
; SetName is privileged -> this script is on Privileged Scripts.dat.

Function Main()

	NPC = Actor()
	SetName(NPC, "Grukk, the Raider-Chief")

	Return

End Function
